n^2 = a^2 + b^2 - 2ab \cos\alpha
\Delta ABC
m^2 = a^2 + b^2 - 2ab \cos(180-\alpha) = a^2 + b^2 + 2ab \cos(\alpha)
\Delta DAC
a^2 = (\frac{m}{2})^2 + (\frac{n}{2})^2 -2 \frac{m}{2} \frac{n}{2} \cos(\beta)
\Delta AEB
b^2 = (\frac{m}{2})^2 + (\frac{n}{2})^2 -2 \frac{m}{2} \frac{n}{2} \cos(180 - \beta)
\Delta BEC
a^2 = \frac{m^2}{4} + \frac{n^2}{4} - \frac{mn \cos(\beta)}{2}
b^2 = \frac{m^2}{4} + \frac{n^2}{4} + \frac{mn \cos(\beta)}{2}
\Rightarrow
